article.headline: Marshall 69, Morehead St. 56
article.story: HUNTINGTON, W.Va. (AP) -- Markel Humphrey scored 16 points and grabbed 10 rebounds to lead Marshall to a 69-56 win over Morehead State on Saturday night. Marshall (4-1) led 34-27 at halftime and scored 20 unanswered points spanning both halves. Morehead State got no closer than five points down the stretch. Mark Dorris added 13 points and Tirrel Baines scored 10 for Marshall. Leon Buchanan led Morehead State (2-4) with 13 points.
